{"tid":1580023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽龍兒獲伯伯送回家 其間更挽着對方手臂","createTime":"2019-09-19T00:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T01:48:57.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f43feebec188fd6f9064b89fe26be06751c80ab8","tid":1580023,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T00:50:04.000Z","msg":"屯門大媽收錢3部曲，首先下午到屯門公園Fan meeting粉絲見面會收利是，然後晚上酒樓包場開P，繼續賣枱收利是，最後就是收兵「求包養」，氹得「鐵粉」照顧日常起居，生活無憂。《蘋果》發現在小月生日會晚宴上，「龍兒」為最受歡迎的年輕大媽，散席後未有放軟手腳，由大叔「鐵粉」邊談心邊送返屋企，平日更有「運輸兵」的士司機變身私人司機管接管送。有資深檔主透露，大媽有足夠人氣，檔主才會找上邀請開工，故大媽們為保障收入都會好好經營一套「收兵策略」。<br />\n<br />\n長髮披肩、溫文爾雅的大媽龍兒，年約40歲，年紀比其他濃妝大媽小一截，她在生日會散席後，由一名居於毗鄰的伯伯結伴回家，二人沿路保持交流，不時細聲講大聲笑，行至一條後巷，她見伯伯顯出疲態，即使自己手挽一個大袋，仍主動挽着伯伯手臂攙扶，只見伯伯甚為受落，充當護花使者回報龍兒好意，直至步行到她家後才分道揚鑣。<br />\n<br />\n光復屯門公園後，龍兒亦少了到歌檔獻唱，記者連日追蹤，發現她平日沒工開，會打扮得樸樸實實，輪流與兩名大叔「鐵粉」飲茶。她每日都相當規律，約中午時出門，然後滿頭白髮、任職的士司機的「運輸兵」早已在樓下等候，然後接載她到酒樓，會合另一名身形高大的中年男飲茶談天，每次都傾足2小時才埋單離開，龍兒亦相當識做，飲茶多數會主動埋單。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190919/60059784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60059784&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5b2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=d71c3a4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60059784&h=f3721a86\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190919/60059784</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190919/large/1568830832_1590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568830832_1590.jpg&h=c9763ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190919/large/1568830832_04a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568830832_04a2.jpg&h=6c956b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無記者在場，打下車輪，chok下賓州，一定有"},{"pid":"f2570fefb31cd8e73af127287280dc8f4c103d65","tid":1580023,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T00:50:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5b2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=d38493c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5b2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=e650dea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"2753dd3536e58b37ebe50a3419b7d24ce970efb0","tid":1580023,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T00:50:52.000Z","msg":"d藍絲廢老真係腦裝屎，臭雞一隻都係咁課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b750d49f6bd6b070bb86377672e825a0a9fe2c2","tid":1580023,"uid":251292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人都做兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比幾百蚊叫雞好過啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4a5d148be67c81c45a681bf0ada86da67d1ae5"